# RicoCoder API Keys Backup — alternative keys in case primary keys expire
# Primary keys are in ~/ricocoder/bridge/bridge_env.sh (sourced via ~/.bashrc)
# This file is sourced AFTER bridge_env.sh as fallback.
# Variables with _BACKUP_n suffix do NOT override primary.
# Variables without suffix override primary — keep synced with bridge_env.sh.

